# Framework Fidelity (LightRAG + RAG-Anything)

## Non-negotiable rules

- All RAG behavior must follow **official LightRAG + RAG-Anything** design and defaults (HKUDS repositories).
- **Do not add reranking** or any reranker step. Do not suggest it.
- **No toggles/flags/optional modes** in our integration code. The system should work end-to-end out-of-the-box.

## Integration guardrails

- Keep LightRAG query routes and default query behavior intact (modes/params/prompts).
- Only override ingestion endpoints when required to route parsing through RAG-Anything.
- Avoid custom query-time prompt injection, keyword hacks, or parameter overrides.

## Primary sources

- LightRAG: `https://github.com/HKUDS/LightRAG`
- RAG-Anything: `https://github.com/HKUDS/RAG-Anything`
